Pantheon synthesis

The three notes converge on the same upgrade:

The Transformation Alphabet should no longer be treated as just a list of moves.
It should now be treated as a reasoning operating system with four layers:
	1.	Operator Library — the moves themselves
	2.	Operator Algebra — how the moves compose, interfere, and fail
	3.	Scale Ladder — how the same moves behave at personal, team, civilizational, and cosmic resolution
	4.	Distortion Governance — what each move costs, when it breaks, and how to recover

That is the real integration point.

