1. Operator Algebra becomes official
This is the biggest upgrade.

The alphabet is no longer just a field manual of isolated moves. It becomes a generative grammar.

Add to Combinatorix’s role:
	•	Composition Table — which move chains are legal, useful, unstable, or self-canceling
	•	Invariant Lattice — partial ordering of what survives across transformations
	•	Equivalence Classes — when two seemingly different chains are secretly the same under relabeling
	•	Chain Distortion Metric — cumulative cost after multiple moves
